\SE[16]It's Cat-chan's shop, you know~. \!\SE[0]If you need
any supplies, feel free to ask~. (It's not free though!)

I'm Hidarii. Despite appearances, we are a group of elite
individuals. We're amazing, you know. Hehe.

I'm Migii. It might be a bit insensitive, but... big
operations really get my blood pumping.

\SE[2]Oh, is it time for Swissy-chan to make an
appearance!? \SE[2]Once we leave, I don't think we'll be
able to come back for a while, but are you prepared?

\SE[16]It's time to set sail...! \!\SE[15]Come on! Get on
board!!
